## Phase 4 Complete (Weeks 1–6)

### Feature Flags (_FEATURE_TIERS)

| Flag | Tiers | Purpose |
|------|-------|---------|
| `hedis_summary` | FREE, PRO | Gap summary (free tier) |
| `hedis_predictions` | PRO | ML predictions, intervention plans |
| `radv_calculator` | PRO | RADV exposure scoring |
| `hcc_scoring` | PRO | RAF, gaps, revenue |
| `stars_calculator` | PRO | QBP threshold, trajectory, command center |

### starguard-core Modules

| Module | Key APIs |
|--------|----------|
| RADV | `default_scenario`, `score_exposure` |
| HCC | `default_hcc_scenario`, `compute_raf_batch`, `identify_chronic_gaps`, `compute_revenue_opportunity` |
| HEDIS | `default_hedis_scenario`, `predict_closure_batch`, `build_intervention_plan` |
| Stars | `default_stars_scenario`, `compute_bonus_threshold_impact`, `project_stars` |
| Command Center | `run_command_center()` — wires all four |

### CI/CD (deploy.yml)

- **Test job**: Always runs (push + PR). Ruff, mypy, pytest.
- **Deploy job**: Only on push to main. Uses `HF_TOKEN` to sync to HuggingFace Space.
- **Mobile**: Pytest runs with `PYTHONPATH=Artifacts/app`; deploy uploads `Artifacts/app/` to Space.
- **Rollback**: `git revert` → push → auto-redeploy. No manual HF intervention.

### Phase 4 Demo Numbers (Locked)

| Metric | Value | Scale |
|--------|-------|-------|
| HCC recapture | $27,625 | Synthetic; scales to plan level |
| HEDIS revenue | $0.66M | 8 gaps; ~$4M+ at 50K members |
| QBP on 3.5→4.0 | $6M+ | 50K members crossing threshold |
| Star points | 17 | From 8 HEDIS gaps |

### Phase 4 Close Gate

```bash
cd starguard-core && python verify_phase4_close_gate.py
```

Expected: All four modules + command center print `[OK]`; exit 0.

